// ── ALBERTA SECTION
// Developer notes:
//   - Profile stored in localStorage key 'huntsmart_ab_profile'
//   - Hunt rows mapped to priority via getAbPriorityKey(draw, species)
//   - Priority comparison: user pts vs min drawn pts in latest year
